Forex education is a multifunctional application for traders that will help you learn the field of trading.

We offer:

- trading courses that give the most important information without water: the material for studying is presented in a compact and simple form;
- checking your knowledge using test forms;
- acutal analytics and forecasts in real time;
- a trading simulator where you can test your own strategies without losing real assets. You start with $10,000 in virtual cash and can make an unlimited number of transactions.
- exchange rates and currency pairs;
- Graphical display of currency changes in real time - select the desired asset and track its changes, the date and time are displayed for each currency.

important: This application is intended for informational and entertainment purposes only. No real deals will ever be made. No real money is involved here. Market data is provided “as is” and their accuracy is not guaranteed.

